    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enigma Isle 是一款处于早期开发阶段的游戏，玩家决定在一个荒岛上生活，可以在岛上耕种、采集、制作、钓鱼以及与航海者交易。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >种植农作物来烹饪食物，以提升玩家属性，并制作鱼饵用于钓鱼。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121230/extras/e11bfee30603b2af96d2a2a0cca36fcd.poster.avif?t=1757113792\" width=480 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121230/extras/e11bfee30603b2af96d2a2a0cca36fcd.webm?t=1757113792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121230/extras/e11bfee30603b2af96d2a2a0cca36fcd.mp4?t=1757113792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的钓鱼玩法！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121230/extras/46888a86a759d775905c8dccf33da0ba.poster.avif?t=1757113792\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121230/extras/46888a86a759d775905c8dccf33da0ba.webm?t=1757113792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121230/extras/46888a86a759d775905c8dccf33da0ba.mp4?t=1757113792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开采矿石以升级你的工具和武器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用你的武器抵御海盗的袭击！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121230/extras/985f642398b0bd2bb05faf0aad9593e4.poster.avif?t=1757113792\" width=480 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps